stimulus:
Calibration Session

Sit comfortably, from now on try to keep your head as still as possible.

Next you will see a series of markers in the screen.
As they appear fix your gaze on them.
Once they turn orange, press the space bar.

stimulus:
Experimentation Session (1 / 1)

1 times you will see a series of stimulus in the same positions in which you just calibrated. Fix your gaze on them as they appear.
A central cross will appear in between each pair of series. While this cross is present you can rest your gaze and blink.
Press the space bar to start.
